features: EXTREME VOLUME, WATERPROOF WEAR: The all-time beauty favorite, the I LOVE EXTREME CRAZY VOLUME mascara from essence, is now available in a waterproof version! With a creamy, waterproof formula and extra-large brush, this mascara delivers mega volume and a bold, dramatic finish.

MEGA-SIZED BRUSH: The unique extra-large elastomer brush works to coat each individual lash, resulting in an intense, volumizing effect with just one stroke! Starting at the base of your lashes, swipe brush from roots to tips and layer until desired effect is achieved.

LONG-LASTING WEAR: The waterproof formula of the I Love Extreme Crazy Volume Waterproof Mascara ensures that your bold, voluminous look lasts all day, no matter what rain, sweat, or tears life throws your way.
CLAIMS: Vegan & Cruelty Free. Free from parabens, fragrance, alcohol, & microplastic particles. Made in Luxembourg.
CRUELTY FREE: essence cosmetics is certified and acknowledged by PETA as a cruelty-free brand. We do not test any of our products on animals.
